data.title: News
data.meta_description:
The one stop shop where genuine and personally signed items of #JonahLomu can be purchased. "It's official and original" said the man himself #Jonhlomu.
We do not guarantee the authenticity of Jonah's autograph when obtained on any other online platform or otherwise claimed by any individuals, companies or collectives.
data.text: Jonah Lomu MNZM, greeted by hundreds of his fans when arriving with his family at Reading Train Station, Berkshire, England, the Global Icon of World Rugby walked straight into the crowds where hundreds awaited his arrival. Many of his fans being youngsters of all ages, the generation of whom had the pleasure of watching and cheering for Jonah as he once set foot onto the playing field creating a roar whenever he was present. Those also including the Police as they joined the queue, not able to resist the chance to meet the great man, stepping in to have photos...
